action.text:
Lenore summons a shimmering wall within 120 feet of her. The wall can be up to 90 feet long, 30 feet high, and 1 inch thick. Alternatively, she can shape the wall into a sphere up to 30 feet in diameter centered on a point she can see within range. The wall has three octarine layers. When a creature attempts to reach into or pass through the wall, it does so one layer at a time through all the wall's layers. Constitution Saving Throw: DC 19. Failure: 
• Layer 1: 10 (3d6) Necrotic damage and the target gains one level of Contamination and has the Dazed condition; 
• Layer 2: 17 (5d6) Necrotic damage, and the target gains two levels of Contamination and has the Defenseless condition; 
• Layer 3: 35 (10d6) Necrotic damage, and the target gains three levels of Contamination and the Helpless condition. 
Success: Half damage only. The wall can be destroyed by taking at least 100 Radiant or Force damage.
